==Notes on use==

This template may be used to externally link to [[eMedicine]] articles.

It requires at least two parameters giving the medical field and topic number, but may optionally have a third parameter giving alternative text of the disease name.

 Hence: <nowiki>{{EMedicine|emerg|43}}</nowiki>
 Gives: {{EMedicine|emerg|43}}

 Whilst <nowiki>{{EMedicine|emerg|43|Asthma}}</nowiki>
 Gives: {{EMedicine|emerg|43|Asthma}}


==eMedicine URLs==
This template configures the url for: <nowiki>http://www.emedicine.com/<<field>>/topic<<topic number>>.htm</nowiki>


